          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "165Er does not emit gammas after its EC decay but can",
                "be quantified by the characteristic X-lines of its",
                "daughter 165Ho.",
                "X-rays with the same energies come after decays of",
                "other simultaneously produced Er radioisotopes and",
                "from internal transitions of isomeric states of",
                "directly produced Ho isotopes as well. As, however,",
                "all these disturbing activities decay with shorter",
                "half lives than 165Er, using a proper cooling time it",
                "is possible to determine the contribution of 165Er",
                "separately."
              ]
            }
          ],
